title: Grateful Dead Live at Hampton Coliseum on 1987-03-23
lineage: Playback Maxell XL-IIS cassette masters on Sony TC-D5m to Marantz PMD-670
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Grey, Little Red Rooster, Althea, Me & My Uncle-> Big River, Iko Iko, Tons Of Steel, Feel Like A Stranger, Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Box Of Rain, Women Are Smarter, Ship of Fools, Truckin'-> Jam-> Drums-> Space-> The Other One-> Stella Blue-> Throwing Stones-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: U.S. Blues

reviews.review_text: - Great sound, and although Garcia is hard to hear up until the 2nd half of the 2nd set, this is rectified later. The show is good.
